wargus (2.4.1-1) unstable; urgency=low

  * Compatibility with Stratagus 2.4.1
  * Updated installers for debian, windows, mac os x
  * Remove remaining maemo support code
  * Features
    - Support lua checksums and add proper error message for multiplayer
    - Make barracks selectable by rectangle
    - Commandline arguments can be passed to directly start or join multiplayer games
  * Bugfixes
    - All buttons now emit click sounds
    - Sapper demolition range increased to behave as in original game
    - Main menu music should now be correct for all supported versions
    - Remove colorcycled border
    - Disable diplomacy checkboxes for computer players
    - Remove unfinished metaserver menu
    - ToD Human mission 4 now rescues rangers, not archers

 -- Tim Felgentreff <timfelgentreff@gmail.com>  Wed, 2 Dec 2015 11:28:27 +0100

